detail.Title: [MV] Flying High - JKT48
detail.Description:
#JKT48FlyingHigh is an expression to celebrate all of the journey and achievements throughout the 10 years of JKT48's existence. Produced by acknowledged producers who have worked with international Western and K-Pop artists - Matt Rad and August Rigo - JKT48 is serving their new era of music to the world!

Enjoy Flying High music video, the 23rd single and also the 2nd original single of JKT48!

These are the nine performing members:
Azizi Asadel
Shani Indira Natio
Feni Fitriyanti
Shania Gracia
Jinan Safa Safira
Angelina Christy

Marsha Lenathea

Let's celebrate Flying High together!
